    <!-- Fixed brand navy: intentionally NOT overridden in values-night, so it
         stays the same navy in both light and dark mode. Used for chrome that
         should read as "this app's brand color" regardless of theme (top bar,
         FAB, the valuation highlight card). This is NOT the same thing as the
         adaptive colorPrimary role, which Material3 deliberately flips to a
         light tone in dark mode for text/icon contrast, not for backgrounds. -->
